name: Pokemon #172: Pichu LV5
text:
(This card is always treated as a "Baby Pokemon" card.)
Once per turn, you can add 1 "Baby Pokemon" monster from your Deck to your hand. You can only use this effect of "Pokemon #172: Pichu" once per turn, and this card cannot attack the turn this effect is activated. If this card is attacked, Flip a coin: If tails, negate the attack. During the Standby Phase of your next turn after this card was Summoned: You can send this card to the GY; Special Summon 1

monster from your hand or Deck.
